      "source": [
        "**Interpretation:** The map reveals that Western Europe functions like a highly interconnected neural network, where countries like the UK generate crises that spread quickly , and countries like Belgium immediately absorb them. Meanwhile, the northern peripheries are shielded and do not actively participate in this domino chain."
      ]
    },
